s://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cenbank-leave-medium-term-rate-unchanged-expected-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>AI芯片需求激增，台积电第二季度利润跃升30%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-second-quarter-profit-seen-jumping-30-surging-ai-chip-demand-2024-07-15/</link><description>人工智能应用先进芯片的主要生产商台积电周四预计，由于需求飙升，第二季度利润将增长 30%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 00:52:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-second-quarter-profit-seen-jumping-30-surging-ai-chip-demand-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国第二季度GDP未达预期，刺激呼声持续高涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-economy-seen-slowing-q2-stimulus-calls-grow-2024-07-14/</link><description>周一的数据显示，中国经济第二季度放缓，房地产市场持续低迷和就业不稳定打压内需，使人们对北京需要推出更多刺激措施的预期依然不减。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:12:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-economy-seen-slowing-q2-stimulus-calls-grow-2024-07-14/</guid></item><item><title>由于工厂关闭和廉价的中国进口商品，泰国经济面临剧变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/thai-economy-faces-upheaval-due-factory-closures-cheap-chinese-imports-2024-07-14/</link><description>当中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪本月早些时候在泰国开设第一家东南亚工厂时，这个拥有6600万人口的国家成为众人瞩目的焦点，并因其工业愿景而赢得赞誉。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:09:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/thai-economy-faces-upheaval-due-factory-closures-cheap-chinese-imports-2024-07-14/</guid></item><item><title>随着市场与美国政治的斗争，美国国债下滑，美元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-14/</link><description>周一，美国债券期货下跌，美元走强，因为投资者押注对美国总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普的攻击将增加他获胜的可能性，同时给市场注入全新水平的政治不确定性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:03:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-14/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：特朗普枪击事件令市场蒙上阴影，中国GDP成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-14/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 21:50:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国和澳大利亚推动世界银行为太平洋岛屿提供美元生命线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/world-bank-dollar-lifeline-pacific-islands-proceeds-with-us-australia-push-2024-07-14/</link><description>世界银行正在美国和澳大利亚的支持下为太平洋岛国准备一条金融生命线，因为西方银行从这个无利可图的市场撤离，引发了人们对中国可能填补这一战略地区真空的担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 18:11:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/world-bank-dollar-lifeline-pacific-islands-proceeds-with-us-australia-push-2024-07-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国媒体称中俄海军在太平洋部分地区进行联合巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-russia-navies-conduct-joint-patrol-parts-pacific-china-media-says-2024-07-14/</link><description>据中国国家电视台中央电视台周日报道，中国和俄罗斯海军编队最近在西太平洋和北太平洋进行了第四次联合海上巡逻。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 07:00:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-russia-navies-conduct-joint-patrol-parts-pacific-china-media-says-2024-07-14/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜金正恩解雇了对新城项目“不负责任”的官员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-sacks-irresponsible-officials-over-new-town-project-2024-07-13/</link><description>朝鲜官方媒体朝中社周日称，朝鲜领导人金正恩已解雇或降职了一些高级官员，因为他们“不负责任”地处理了朝鲜北部建设新城的旗舰项目。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 23:42:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-sacks-irresponsible-officials-over-new-town-project-2024-07-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责美国涉藏争端法案，誓言捍卫自身利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-blasts-us-tibet-china-dispute-bill-vows-defend-its-interests-2024-07-13/</link><description>中国周六对美国总统乔·拜登签署的一项美国法律表示强烈反对，该法律敦促北京解决西藏要求更大自治权的争端，并誓言“坚定捍卫”其利益。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 09:45:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-blasts-us-tibet-china-dispute-bill-vows-defend-its-interests-2024-07-13/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称机构抢购中国国债正在做空经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/institutions-snapping-up-chinese-treasury-bonds-are-shorting-economy-state-media-2024-07-13/</link><description>中国央行支持的《金融时报》周六援引行业消息人士和专家的观点报道称，金融机构抢购中国国债基本上是在做空中国经济。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 08:02:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/institutions-snapping-up-chinese-treasury-bonds-are-shorting-economy-state-media-2024-07-13/</guid></item><item><title>商务部副部长会见沃尔玛首席执行官麦克雷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-vice-commerce-ministry-meets-walmart-ceo-mclay-2024-07-13/</link><description>中国商务部在一份声明中称，中国商务部副部长王受文周五会见了沃尔玛公司首席执行官凯瑟琳·麦克莱。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 06:42:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-vice-commerce-ministry-meets-walmart-ceo-mclay-2024-07-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>